          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Small Business Relief from Disease Induced Economic Hardship Act of 2016</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Small Business Act with respect to Small Business Administration disaster assistance to expand the definition of &quot;disaster&quot; to include the onset of transmissible diseases for which the federal government issues a public health advisory or declaration.</p>]]></text>
